<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","className":"paragraph-custom-size","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.75rem"}},"fontFamily":"system-sans-serif"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center paragraph-custom-size has-system-sans-serif-font-family" style="font-size:1.75rem">The faculty members featured on this site are official members of the Brooklyn College Department of Computer and Information Science.&nbsp;They offer incomparable expertise and tremendous talent, and each brings a unique perspective to their teaching and mentoring in and out of the classroom.</p>
