<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.25rem"}},"fontFamily":"system-sans-serif"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-system-sans-serif-font-family" style="font-size:1.25rem">Begin your Tableau for Students journey.<br>In the world of ever-changing AI and technology, we know learning a new tool can feel overwhelming. Follow this recommended guide to jumpstart your Tableau skill building and learn about the community.</p>
