<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.25rem"}},"fontFamily":"system-sans-serif"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-system-sans-serif-font-family" style="font-size:1.25rem">Become a Friends of Figma user group leader.Leaders are the heart and soul of our global community. They go above and beyond to give back to the Figma community by passionately running our Friends of Figma groups, helping people to connect and learn from one another.&nbsp;</p>
