<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.25rem"}},"fontFamily":"system-sans-serif"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-system-sans-serif-font-family" style="font-size:1.25rem">The City University of New York is the nation’s largest urban public university, a transformative engine of social mobility that is a critical component of the lifeblood of New York City. Founded in 1847 as the nation’s first free public institution of higher education, CUNY today has&nbsp;26 colleges&nbsp;spread across New York City’s five boroughs.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:column -->

