<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"1.25rem"}},"fontFamily":"system-sans-serif"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-system-sans-serif-font-family" style="font-size:1.25rem">Connect with Industry<br>Millions of engineers and scientists rely on MATLAB and Simulink in a&nbsp;wide range of applications and industries. You’ll become part of the global MATLAB community and gain essential professional experience by working with a leading technical computing software company while still in college.</p>
