<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Question"},"align":"full","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontSize":"large","fontFamily":"optifranklingothic-medium"} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull has-optifranklingothic-medium-font-family has-large-font-size" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>Is CIS Connect free to use?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>Yes! All you need to do is log in with your school email to have access to the website.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>
<!-- /wp:details -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"50px"} -->
<div style="height:50px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontFamily":"franklin-gothic-atf"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignfull has-franklin-gothic-atf-font-family" id="job-internship" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px">Job &amp; Internship Search</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"50px"} -->
<div style="height:50px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Question"},"align":"full","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontSize":"large","fontFamily":"optifranklingothic-medium"} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull has-optifranklingothic-medium-font-family has-large-font-size" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>What types of job and internship opportunities are listed on CIS Connect?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>The jobs and internships shared on our website will cover a wide range of specializations, including software development, database administration, and game design.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>
<!-- /wp:details -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"20px"} -->
<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Question"},"align":"full","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontSize":"large","fontFamily":"optifranklingothic-medium"} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull has-optifranklingothic-medium-font-family has-large-font-size" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>How often are new job and internship postings posted?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>We will try to update the website with new job and internship postings at least twice a week.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>
<!-- /wp:details -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"50px"} -->
<div style="height:50px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontFamily":"franklin-gothic-atf"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignfull has-franklin-gothic-atf-font-family" id="resume-portfolio" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px">Resume &amp; Portfolio</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"50px"} -->
<div style="height:50px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Question"},"align":"full","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontSize":"large","fontFamily":"optifranklingothic-medium"} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull has-optifranklingothic-medium-font-family has-large-font-size" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>What should my resume look like?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>See the <a href="https://testingcis.commons.gc.cuny.edu/resume-templates/" data-type="page" data-id="1235">Resume Templates Page</a> for more information on how to improve your resume. This page also includes multiple templates for you to use.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>
<!-- /wp:details -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"20px"} -->
<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Question"},"align":"full","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontSize":"large","fontFamily":"optifranklingothic-medium"} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull has-optifranklingothic-medium-font-family has-large-font-size" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>What should my Portfolio look like? Where should I store it?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>You should use a project repository like GitHub to store the code for any side projects you do. That way, employers can have an easy time finding your work.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>
<!-- /wp:details -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"50px"} -->
<div style="height:50px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontFamily":"franklin-gothic-atf"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignfull has-franklin-gothic-atf-font-family" id="support" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px">Support</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"50px"} -->
<div style="height:50px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer -->

<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Question"},"align":"full","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}},"fontSize":"large","fontFamily":"optifranklingothic-medium"} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull has-optifranklingothic-medium-font-family has-large-font-size" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>Who do I contact if I'm having trouble with the website?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>See the <a href="https://testingcis.commons.gc.cuny.edu/contact/" data-type="page" data-id="1111">Contact Page</a> for more information on how to resolve any issues you may have with the website.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>
<!-- /wp:details -->

<!-- wp:spacer -->
<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>
